e "cheesecake" spread and sliced strawberries with graham crackers is the perfect combination for a dessert.  Rich so save some room for this dessert. - Creme Brulee - The caramelized sugar inside of this waffle completes the dessert.  Similar to the Strawberry cheesecake because this too includes strawberry slices. Their shakes and sodas are also one of a kind.  The shakes are super thick and soda flavors yummy.  I liked their Frozen custard too.  Imagine ice cream but better. Tons to love at Bruxie!  Try their newer location in Downtown Brea!  More seating.
