erything is ok and take your empty tray right when you're done with it. Very attentive! Such nice servers as well! We had quite the surprise at the end of our meal. We were cleaning up when one of the servers brought us a mint chocolate chip shake! I was take aback because I didn't order it. The server said there was extra so he just gave it to us! Wow! What a lucky day for us! :) 4 stars only. I would have given five if I had liked the bruxie burger a little more, if there wasn't so much mist (I swear it's on MAX), and the sogginess from the juices. However, it was an enjoyable experience and an upgrade from fast food. I will come back to try the Buttermilk Fried Chicken!
