nd it was delicious!  It's something so simple but so tasty.  My friend also let me try the strawberry creme brulee waffle and that thing is delicious goodness!  I was almost tempted to buy one myself but I was at a satisfied full.  I will definitely go here again, the food is awesome and the customer service is on point! *No bathrooms *Accepts credit cards
